<BYLINE>
<P>
By BERT ELJERA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Work began this week on a $980,000 project to install storm drains along Trask 
Avenue between Harbor Boulevard and Fairview Street, city officials said. 
</P>
