<TEXT>
<P>
 Entrepreneur Ideas: The Home Office & Small Business Assn. has introduced a 
monthly newsletter designed to give entrepreneurs ideas for advertising and 
marketing. 
</P>
<P>
 "Most advertising agencies are not in a position to work for small companies 
with small budgets," said Pam Lindemann, marketing and sales director for the 
Winter Park, Fla., organization. "This newsletter fills that gap." 
</P>
<P>
 Cost of the newsletter is $29 for a 12-month subscription. For more 
information, call the association at (800) 260-9523. 
